headline.print_headline: Police in Tobago Investigate Murder of German Couple on Beach
headline.main: Police in Tobago Investigate Murder of German Couple on Beach

lead_paragraph: Police are investigating the murder of an elderly German couple found hacked to death on a beach near their home in the southern Caribbean island of Tobago on Saturday.
